songs.title: Marilyn
songs.lyrics:
Are you feeling lucky tonight?
Marilyn, Marilyn, Marilyn
Marilyn, Marilyn, Marilyn, Marilyn
Are you wearing nothing tonight, Marilyn?
Marilyn, Marilyn
Marilyn, Marilyn
Marilyn
Are you blessing somebody tonight?
Are you blessing?

Have you ever seen Downtown New Orleans, that's where I'm from
That's were I've been, where I was made
Somewhere laying in between
Marilyn, Marilyn
Marilyn, Marilyn
